name: SVGFEBlendElement
description: The SVGFEBlendElement interface corresponds to the <feBlend> element.

members.name: SVGFEBlendElement.in1
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEBlendElement.in2
members.description: An SVGAnimatedString corresponding to the in2 attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFEBlendElement.mode
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the mode attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_FEBLEND_MODE_* constants defined on this interface.
